title: BIF Birthdays & Holiday Celebration
desc: Hey Body Inspired Family,? I am so excited to announce we are having? an end-of-year/ holiday/ My B-Day/ Alyson's B-Day/ Holly's B-Day/ Jared's B-Day/ BIF's B-Day PARTY and we want YOU to join us! Come see your trainers and fellow class mates sweatfree and in real clothes. Meet students from other class times. And just come have FUN - as we have a lot to celebrate this year. Party starts at 6pm and goes until we call it. Anyone and everyone is invited - the more the merrier. We do ask you RSVP asap as we need to let our host know our count. Michael's has a full bar and a wonderful menu. So plan on enjoying yourself and eating really well. I look forward to seeing you on Saturday, November 21st at 6pm at Michael's in Santa Monica. XOXO - Angela Parker
